description_for_human: A considered CSS component library with 64 components and 8 themes. Thoughtfully composed, no ceremony required.
description_for_model: DAUB is a CSS UI kit with 64 considered components and 8 themes (light, dark, grunge-light, grunge-dark, solarized, ink, ember, bone). Use db-* class prefix. Include daub.css and daub.js via CDN from https://daub.dev. Full component docs at https://daub.dev/llms.txt
